-- Italy Government Members Belonging to Fini's Party Offer Resignations
-- B y   M a r c o   B e r t a c c h e
-- 2010-11-07T11:30:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-07/italy-government-members-belonging-to-fini-s-party-offer-resignations.html
Members of the new Future and Liberty
political party founded by Gianfranco Fini, Prime Minister
Silvio Berlusconi’s ally, offered their resignations subject to
Fini’s decision, Deputy Industry Minister Adolfo Urso
said in Perugia today.  His comment were broadcast by RAINews state television.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Marco Bertacche at 
 mbertacche@bloomberg.net  